snippet.title: Heartbreak High: A Break-Up Simulator (TRAILER)
snippet.description:
Heartbreak High is an arcade-style twist on the dating sim genre where you're the most popular student in school, you're dating everyone in your class, and you're breaking up with them one by one.

BUY IT ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/836350/Heartbreak_High_A_BreakUp_Simulator/

BUY IT ON ITCH.IO:
https://alecrobbins.itch.io/heartbreakhigh

http://goodbit.biz
